,{"pid":"180a90ff0f0ec7bffda5ddcb2c00966de958187d","tid":12913,"uid":41176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T15:29:15.000Z","msg":"久米島個沙灘好正 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n內陸機都係30分鐘就到<br />\n但唔渣車久米島玩唔到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"480002622eedc2254d7c87b9c4a21f4e945522b3","tid":12913,"uid":41176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T15:30:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>久米島個沙灘好正 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n內陸機都係30分鐘就到<br />\n但唔渣車久米島玩唔到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n自 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n揸車"},{"pid":"ea49b23f6a81bfc9eed76dbc61f3be8f75a0dbf5","tid":12913,"uid":36278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T15:33:07.000Z","msg":"有無巴打可以幫下忙俾意見，十年無坐飛機，真係好苦，岩岩出黎做野先去旅行"},{"pid":"79c19c33f28b4c2014f2c8222e04ee9ad4b1151f","tid":12913,"uid":36278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T15:33:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>久米島個沙灘好正 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n內陸機都係30分鐘就到<br />\n但唔渣車久米島玩唔到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n自 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n揸車</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c185743e51909c1eafa7b5c8659edf14181dd4f7","tid":12913,"uid":36278,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T02:26:05.000Z","msg":"有無巴打有去過"},{"pid":"9130083d5a656e0c4778297256626e8fdafabb98","tid":12913,"uid":41083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T02:34:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>小弟5日4夜，有無咩建議，女朋友要去潛水，如果去萬座毛，今歸仁城跡，有無時間上北部同水族館</blockquote><br />\n二月去潛水唔會凍咩？</blockquote><br />\n一，二月又大風又凍喎， 巴打肯定要落水？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68467a2e422d20552519ef839ab7baad12793bc7","tid":12913,"uid":41083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T02:37:29.000Z","msg":"btw 我冇潛水， 所有唔熟， 不過你可以google下有冇鋪頭有2月潛水團， 好似有個好靚既潛水地方叫青洞。"},{"pid":"994d3979c4abd5824934a9f703e0c4b220f6075f","tid":12913,"uid":41083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T02:49:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都spend 兩日係那霸市同豐見市，之後上美國村，殘波岬，琉球村，萬座毛，水族館，古宇利島反黎，係咪5日4夜無可能，有無咩地方可以唔去</blockquote><br />\n 我想問巴打係咪自駕？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n下面係我個人自駕既經驗<br />\n<br />\n五日四夜， 我會分開上下兩邊玩， 兩晚住那霸， 兩日住恩納/美國村/名護果頭。<br />\n <br />\n我上次就簡住恩納， 因為恩納上名護去水族館，落美國村，去古宇利島都係一個鐘左右。<br />\n<br />\n去殘波岬都係less than 30mins， 萬座毛直程係附近"},{"pid":"1dccec18c96cf1dbfca8f32d0571350630b76b85","tid":12913,"uid":26998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T02:52:22.000Z","msg":"岩岩去完石垣返黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n兩年前都係呢段時間去左浮潛加潛水<br />\n個教練話全年都可以浮潛/潛水<br />\n但係冬天會大浪好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n去青洞果次大浪到我以為我會死係海<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n水族館琉球村古宇利島我係一日去晒<br />\n因為join左local tour，唔貴，無車牌可以諗諗<br />\n青洞真係好靚，好值得去<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6SH57mL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6SH57mL.jpg&h=8489ee25&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/14/105147_f864a8a87358aa7954a6865184335131.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F14%2F105147_f864a8a87358aa7954a6865184335131.jpg&h=084fbbb4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/14/105134_eae84f69e93cb0b269c7bbe5c63b9256.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F14%2F105134_eae84f69e93cb0b269c7bbe5c63b9256.jpg&h=0cf5751e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"29f26b9385eeb8d728f451c2acca7c8f125f98d7","tid":12913,"uid":36278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T02:52:27.000Z","msg":"係呀，有無咩一定要remarks，一定去之類<br />\nbtw <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba33689a7d9c2edd6d2f26a76e286c1eef3a840e","tid":12913,"uid":36278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T02:53:43.000Z","msg":"巴打有愛，有無人明二十幾歲人終於有女朋友去旅行個滋味"},{"pid":"e89fc6a2085ab55f30bbca409323f05bc05490ae","tid":12913,"uid":41083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T02:54:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>岩岩去完石垣返黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n兩年前都係呢段時間去左浮潛加潛水<br />\n個教練話全年都可以浮潛/潛水<br />\n但係冬天會大浪好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n去青洞果次大浪到我以為我會死係海<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n水族館琉球村古宇利島我係一日去晒<br />\n因為join左local tour，唔貴，無車牌可以諗諗<br />\n青洞真係好靚，好值得去<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6SH57mL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6SH57mL.jpg&h=8489ee25&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/14/105147_f864a8a87358aa7954a6865184335131.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F14%2F105147_f864a8a87358aa7954a6865184335131.jpg&h=084fbbb4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/14/105134_eae84f69e93cb0b269c7bbe5c63b9256.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F14%2F105134_eae84f69e93cb0b269c7bbe5c63b9256.jpg&h=0cf5751e&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"663c0ed482e3450f416db296f242faee7d8f4a40","tid":12913,"uid":41083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T02:55:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打有愛，有無人明二十幾歲人終於有女朋友去旅行個滋味</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔明呀 有無人明二十幾歲人都仲係冇女朋友個滋味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3c498e38e0d63209c34bc82b38004c69a61c1df","tid":12913,"uid":26998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T02:57:01.000Z","msg":"我上網睇另一個多人去既潛點叫宮城砂邊，好似近美國村，果道就睇魚多既，未去過所以唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢次去石垣竹富島d相<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係好撚鍾意沖繩<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/14/105338_72ecfdf4b18d2133f568534665611379.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F14%2F105338_72ecfdf4b18d2133f568534665611379.jpg&h=4354a0f9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G4i35J1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG4i35J1.jpg&h=3e7886d2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e26a8a437b208e92c0d1e363d2e539aa0c00a6ee","tid":12913,"uid":30850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T03:27:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>岩岩去完石垣返黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n兩年前都係呢段時間去左浮潛加潛水<br />\n個教練話全年都可以浮潛/潛水<br />\n但係冬天會大浪好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n去青洞果次大浪到我以為我會死係海<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n水族館琉球村古宇利島我係一日去晒<br />\n因為join左local tour，唔貴，無車牌可以諗諗<br />\n青洞真係好靚，好值得去<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6SH57mL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6SH57mL.jpg&h=8489ee25&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/14/105147_f864a8a87358aa7954a6865184335131.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F14%2F105147_f864a8a87358aa7954a6865184335131.jpg&h=084fbbb4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/14/105134_eae84f69e93cb0b269c7bbe5c63b9256.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F14%2F105134_eae84f69e93cb0b269c7bbe5c63b9256.jpg&h=0cf5751e&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n嘩，勁靚！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a06d92ab65c029ba7a78d47cb8513b479cb5a31","tid":12913,"uid":36278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T03:27:57.000Z","msg":"有無多d 好食好玩必買既手信"},{"pid":"511b3675d9b914411ee896d81bd124ee0803233e","tid":12913,"uid":36278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T07:57:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}